    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, original shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained, ensuring the engine runs perfectly and the transmission shifts with factory-new precision. This is a rare opportunity to own a car that has been kept in climate-controlled storage and treated with the utmost care, making it a true collector-grade example.",
