    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to be listing this beauty. If you\u2019ve been looking for a car that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one! It has been my absolute pride and joy, meticulously cared for and kept in pristine condition\u2014seriously, it's flawless. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Come swing by and see it for yourself; you're going to fall in love the moment you sit inside!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six and a 6-speed Getrag manual. This example is mechanically pristine, with documented preventative maintenance including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with VAC coated shells, and rear subframe reinforcement. The individual throttle bodies provide razor-sharp throttle response, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. With zero bolster wear and a flawless exterior, this is a turn-key collector piece for the true enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "2022 model. Single owner. Garage kept. Original paint. No scratches or dents. Interior like new. Full service records included.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality 2015 Porsche Cayman S in Carrara White over Agate Grey leather. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows zero signs of wear. The paint is flawless, protected by a full-body ceramic coating, and retains its original factory luster without a single rock chip or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the leather is supple with no bolstering wear, and the interior is smoke-free. Mechanically, the car is perfect, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio from authorized Porsche centers. With only 12,000 miles, this example features the 20-inch Carrera S wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in pristine showroom condition and reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered on the secondary market. This unit boasts a flawless exterior finish and a meticulously curated interior, entirely free from discernible wear. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a factory-new model, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure absolute operational integrity. For the discerning buyer seeking an uncompromising automotive investment, this specimen represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it really shows in every little detail. No scratches, no dents, and a spotless interior that still has that new-car feel. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with a dual-VANOS system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, both exhibiting zero lash or mechanical fatigue. The chassis integrity is absolute; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with fresh bushings and dampers. Every fluid line is dry, and the individual throttle bodies are perfectly synchronized. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
